0.2.3cvs
========

- Add icons for mute/unmute and talking status
- Improved the player list, turned it into a proper view
- Make main window remember size and position, and the split between log/userlist

0.2.2
=====

- Make server log include date/time
- Use QObject::sender() for signals
- Refactored the code to remove m_, and use static_cast<> and friends
- Make messages track source, so the player who initiated kick/mute/deaf of others is known to all.
- Check version on startup
- Show version in mainwidow
- Add log window on the left
- Reduce dependencies in MainWindow.h
- Store list of servers in connect dialog
- Added persistant database
- Added CHANGES file
